 id="aspace_1ef96463771e91987bf0534c05a4099b" level="item"><did><unittitle>N.Y.O. &amp; W. train with Engine No. 68 with two railroad men in front. Undated.</unittitle><container id="aspace_a5bb44cc15603da9f9a54ce9b5740959" label="Mixed Materials [31924065254546]" type="manuscript box">80 - Folder 1</container></did></c01><c01 id="aspace_cbd411fa425bad56f807b77d984e21de" level="item"><did><unittitle>Engine with "Pittston" and L.V.R. on the front. Undated.</unittitle><container id="aspace_0f22a8a3622a6c6a006b2a642f76b858" label="Mixed Materials [31924065254546]" type="manuscript box">80 - Folder 1</container></did></c01><c01 id="aspace_de17f9a4ef4e208f9481f6433f1c7e93" level="item"><did><unittitle>Engine with four men in front and one in the engine. Undated.</unittitle><container id="aspace_7fbdfbf5005b3b16f3460592ac163edd" label="Mixed Materials [31924065254546]" type="manuscript box">80 - Folder 1</container></did></c01></dsc>
